text: Axel Östrand (15 May 1909 - 11 May 2005) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Örnsköldsvik Municipality
